Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: IncludeGarage! Experience the best of city living in this rarely available townhouse-style condominium, offering the space and feel of a single-family home in vibrant South Boston. Spanning four levels and over 2,100 square feet, this 3+ bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence features direct garage parking and a private entrance. Designed for both comfort and entertaining, the open-concept main level boasts a chef’s kitchen with stainless steel appliances, surround sound, and seamless flow into the dining and living areas—complete with a cozy gas fireplace. The top-floor primary suite is a private retreat, featuring a spacious walk-in closet, an ensuite bath, and an exclusive roof deck with stunning city views. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, hardwood floors throughout, a heated driveway, and closet and storage space. Just steps from West Broadway’s top restaurants, shops, and the Red Line.. Currently rented for $6,250, tenant willing to leave early or extend lease for investor
